OL,3,CMan who strangled woman to death with
OL,4,Ctv wire jailed
OL,6,FA Leeds man who strangled and killed
OL,7,Fhis girlfriend with a TV wire has been
OL,8,Fjailed.
OL,10,FGeorge Chalmers, 54, murdered his
OL,11,Fpartner of six months Ruth Baker at
OL,12,Fhis flat in Tempest Road, Beeston, in
OL,13,FMarch this year.
OL,15,FHe finally pleaded guilty to murder
OL,16,Fand assault occasioning actual bodily
OL,17,Fharm on Wednesday and Leeds Crown
OL,18,FCourt heard how he had violently and
OL,19,Fviciously attacked Ruth after a night
OL,20,Fof drinking.
