OL,4,Ctv wire jailed
OL,6,FThe court heard it was not the first
OL,7,Ftime Chalmers had assaulted Ruth, who
OL,8,Fhad given him a second chance. In
OL,9,FNovember last year, she was left with
OL,10,Fbruising and black eyes after he
OL,11,Fattacked her during a romantic getaway
OL,12,Fclose to her home in Carlisle.
OL,14,FChalmers, of Tempest Road, Leeds was
OL,15,Fjailed for a minimum term of 17 years
OL,16,Fand six months at Leeds Crown Court
OL,17,Ftoday (30 October) for the murder of
OL,18,FRuth Baker at his house earlier this
OL,19,Fyear.
