OL,6,FRecorder of Leeds His Honour Judge Guy
OL,7,FKearl, said: "Ruth Baker was aged 48.
OL,8,FShe was killed by you. She was a
OL,9,Fmother, a grandmother and at the time
OL,10,Fyou killed her she lived with her
OL,11,Fyoungest daughter.
OL,13,F"This was a sustained attack where
OL,14,Fphysical injuries were inflicted upon
OL,15,Fher. You have a history of violence
OL,16,Ftowards women. It can only be
OL,17,Fdescribed as a savage and brutal
OL,18,Fattack."
