OL,4,Ctv wire jailed
OL,6,FSpeaking after sentencing, Senior
OL,7,FInvestigating Officer Detective
OL,8,FSuperintendent Emma Winfield, said:
OL,9,F"Our sympathies remain with the family
OL,10,Fof Ruth Baker at this very sad time.
OL,12,F"We hope that they can take some
OL,13,Fcomfort in knowing that Chalmers has
OL,14,Fnow been jailed for life."
OL,16,FRuth's family issued a statement
OL,17,Furging 'people who find themselves
OL,18,Fstuck in an unsafe relationship to
OL,19,Ffind the strength to seek out support
OL,20,Fand find bravery to out before they
OL,21,Ftoo are taken from us unnecessarily.'
